The pipe

Krai |&gt; 
  cry_now()

is the same as

cry_now(Krai)



Krai |&gt;
  cry_now() |&gt; 
  sing_a_song(name = "ABC")

is the same as

sing_a_song(cry_now(Krai),name = "ABC")

